title: PSTS Tanjungbalai
text: Persatuan Sepakbola Tanjungbalai dan Sekitarnya (<a href="English%20language">en</a>: "Football Association Tanjungbalai and surrounding") or PSTS Tanjungbalai is an <a href="Indonesia">Indonesia</a>n <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Tanjungbalai%20%28city%29">Tanjungbalai</a>, <a href="North%20Sumatra">North Sumatra</a>. Club currently played in <a href="Liga%203%20%28Indonesia%29">Liga 3</a>.
